<plot>A documentary film dedicated to the families of foreign soldiers who died in Italy during the Second World War. The "white pastures" (bianchi pascoli) are the Allied War Cemeteries in Italy. The film follows the same path as the Allied all the way through Italy : from the landing in Sicily to the Alps.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?068578</url></doc>
